              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Key Business Insights</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Overall employee attrition rate is </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>16.1%</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Sales</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> department has the highest attrition rate (</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>20.6%</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>). </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Sales Representatives</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> experience the highest attrition (</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>39.8%</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>). </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Employees working overtime are </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>almost three times more likely</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> to leave than those who do not.</run>
